      just the 3rd slot is empty","comment":null,"color":{"r":0.0,"g":0.0,"b":0.0,"a":1.0},"guid":"b559b96e-769f-4fc9-bdd6-f5ec679de277","$version":"A","$type":"Unity.VisualScripting.GraphGroup"},{"position":{"xMin":-982.0,"yMin":1565.0,"xMax":-378.0,"yMax":2086.0},"label":"when
